OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1778674273
OL,3,CFamily calls for change after waiting
OL,4,Cmonths for late father's cancer
OL,5,Cdiagnosis
OL,7,FThe family of an "amazing dad" are
OL,8,Fcalling for urgent change after he
OL,9,Ffaced delays getting a diagnosis for a
OL,10,Fcancer which eventually took his life.
OL,12,FDavid Quayle, a firefighter from the
OL,13,FIsle of Man, first sought medical help
OL,14,Fin 2025 after experiencing back pain,
OL,15,Fbut despite multiple GP appointments
OL,16,Fit took months for him to be diagnosed
OL,17,Fwith Non-Hodgkin Lymphoma.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
