FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1778674273
OL,3,CFamily calls for change after waiting
OL,4,Cmonths for late father's cancer
OL,5,Cdiagnosis
OL,7,FDavid's family are now calling for
OL,8,Furgent change at the island's health
OL,9,Fservice Manx Care, and believe an
OL,10,Fearlier diagnoses could have saved his
OL,11,Flife.
OL,13,FDavid's wife Angela said: "He did
OL,14,Fthink he was going to die. We kept
OL,15,Fsupporting him saying 'you're going to
OL,16,Fbe fine, you just need the right
OL,17,Ftreatment'. How wrong was I?"
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1778674273
OL,3,CFamily calls for change after waiting
OL,4,Cmonths for late father's cancer
OL,5,Cdiagnosis
OL,7,FAs David's pain intensified, his
OL,8,Ffamily took him to A&E in September,
OL,9,Fwhere a CT scan finally found evidence
OL,10,Fof lymphoma.
OL,12,FAngela said: "He'd gone from being
OL,13,Fable to stand up to wheelchair-bound
OL,14,Fin 24 hours. I was terrified to leave
OL,15,Fhim at the hospital, I just didn't
OL,16,Ffeel he was safe in their care."
OL,26,@tD@NOUxD@`O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1778674273
OL,3,CFamily calls for change after waiting
OL,4,Cmonths for late father's cancer
OL,5,Cdiagnosis
OL,7,FWith no ward space available and his
OL,8,Fhealth deteriorating, David waited
OL,9,Fdays for an MRI scan and was
OL,10,Feventually transferred to
OL,11,FClatterbridge Cancer Centre on the
OL,12,FWirral.
OL,14,FAngela said: "At that point the relief
OL,15,Fwas just immense, because I actually
OL,16,Ffelt he was going to be in the right
OL,17,Fplace and receive the treatment he so
OL,18,Furgently needed months before."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1778674273
OL,3,CFamily calls for change after waiting
OL,4,Cmonths for late father's cancer
OL,5,Cdiagnosis
OL,7,FWhen David's condition worsened, he
OL,8,Fwas moved to the Royal Liverpool
OL,9,FHospital, where a chest infection
OL,10,Fstopped further treatment. David died
OL,11,Fjust before Christmas.
OL,13,FAngela said: "He was just an amazing
OL,14,Fdad, I couldn't have asked for a
OL,15,Fbetter father for my children. He was
OL,16,Fthere for them all the time, whatever
OL,17,Fhe could do for them he would do."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1778674273
OL,3,CFamily calls for change after waiting
OL,4,Cmonths for late father's cancer
OL,5,Cdiagnosis
OL,7,FDavid's family received an outpouring
OL,8,Fof condolences from across the Isle of
OL,9,FMan, which Angela said showed just how
OL,10,Floved he was.
OL,12,FShe said: "We've got so many
OL,13,Fcondolence cards and so many messages
OL,14,Fabout how he's helped them."
OL,16,FDavid's brother John said: "I've lost
OL,17,Fa brother, Angie's lost her husband.
OL,18,FThe kids have lost their dad, and so
OL,19,Fmany people have lost a really good
OL,20,Ffriend."
OL,26,@xD@\OU|D@HO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1778674273
OL,3,CFamily calls for change after waiting
OL,4,Cmonths for late father's cancer
OL,5,Cdiagnosis
OL,7,FThe family believe that had David been
OL,8,Ftreated when he first raised concerns,
OL,9,Fhe might still be alive today.
OL,11,FAngela has since met with Manx Care
OL,12,Fbut says more must be done to prevent
OL,13,Fother families from facing similar
OL,14,Fheartbreak.
OL,16,FShe said: "We believe he'd be alive
OL,17,Ftoday if he'd been treated sooner."
OL,19,FSince David's story, work has been
OL,20,Fundertaken to address earlier
OL,21,Fdiagnoses across the Isle of Man.
OL,26,@xD@KOUyD@cO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1778674273
OL,3,CFamily calls for change after waiting
OL,4,Cmonths for late father's cancer
OL,5,Cdiagnosis
OL,7,FIn March 2026, Manx Care asked all GPs
OL,8,Fto adopt Jess's Rule, which encourages
OL,9,Fclinicians to reflect, review and
OL,10,Frethink a diagnosis when a patient
OL,11,Fpresents with the same symptoms on
OL,12,Fthree occasions.
OL,14,FThe Quayle family hopes sharing
OL,15,FDavid's story will prompt further
OL,16,Fchange in the island's healthcare
OL,17,Fsystem, so that no family has to
OL,18,Fendure the same pain.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1778674273
OL,3,CFamily calls for change after waiting
OL,4,Cmonths for late father's cancer
OL,5,Cdiagnosis
OL,7,FIn a joint statement, Manx Care and
OL,8,Fthe Department of Health and Social
OL,9,FCare said they could not comment on
OL,10,Findividual cases, but have recently
OL,11,Fbrought the NHS initiative "Jess'
OL,12,FRule", which encourages clinicians to
OL,13,Freconsider diagnoses when a patient
OL,14,Fpresents with recurring symptoms.
OL,16,FThe statement said: "While reflective
OL,17,Fpractice is already a core part of
OL,18,Fclinical care, this step reinforces
OL,19,Fthe shared commitment to delivering
OL,20,Fsafer and more consistent care across
OL,21,Fthe Island."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1778674273
OL,3,CFamily calls for change after waiting
OL,4,Cmonths for late father's cancer
OL,5,Cdiagnosis
OL,7,FIt continued: "Manx Care and the
OL,8,FDepartment of Health and Social Care
OL,9,Frecognise and value the
OL,10,Fprofessionalism and dedication of
OL,11,Ffrontline staff, who are central to
OL,12,Fdelivering safe, high-quality care.
OL,14,F"Both organisations are committed to
OL,15,Fensuring that staff perspectives are
OL,16,Flistened to and reflected in decision-
OL,17,Fmaking, alongside maintaining strong
OL,18,Fcollaboration between professional and
OL,19,Foperational leadership.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39611
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1778674273
OL,3,CFamily calls for change after waiting
OL,4,Cmonths for late father's cancer
OL,5,Cdiagnosis
OL,7,F"There is a shared focus on
OL,8,Fstrengthening governance and openness
OL,9,Facross services, including promoting
OL,10,Fthe mechanisms available for staff to
OL,11,Fraise concerns and supporting a
OL,12,Fculture that promotes transparency and
OL,13,Fmutual professional respect.
OL,15,F"Manx Care continues to operate a
OL,16,Fclinician-led model, with health and
OL,17,Fsocial work colleagues playing a key
OL,18,Frole in shaping care delivery,
OL,19,Fsupported by experienced managers who
OL,20,Fare equally committed to patients,
OL,21,Fservice users and the community.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39612
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1778674273
OL,3,CFamily calls for change after waiting
OL,4,Cmonths for late father's cancer
OL,5,Cdiagnosis
OL,7,F"Regarding the concerns raised about a
OL,8,Fspecific patient case, both the
OL,9,FDepartment and Manx Care reiterate
OL,10,Fthat they are unable to comment on
OL,11,Findividual circumstances. However,
OL,12,Ffamilies are encouraged to contact the
OL,13,FManx Care Advice and Liaison Service
OL,14,F(MCALS), which provides a formal route
OL,15,Ffor concerns to be raised and fully
OL,16,Finvestigated."
OL,18,FWant more on the issues affecting the
OL,19,FNorth? Our podcast, From the North
OL,20,Fanswers the questions that matter to
OL,21,Four region.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/12
